Package net.getcloudengine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CloudEngine
    This class needs to be instantiated and initialized by every app at the beginning of its execution, typically in the onCreate method of its main activity.
    CloudFile
    Class to represent a file on the disk.
    CloudObject
    All data objects are stored as instances of this class.
    CloudPushService  
    CloudQuery
    CloudQuery class allows the user to query for CloudObjects satisfying a particular condition.
    CloudUser
    Class to represent an app user.
    DeleteCallback
    Callback function for CloudObject delete operations
    FetchCallback
    Callback function for CloudObject fetch operations.
    FindCallback
    Callback function for CloudObject query operations.
    GetCallback
    Callback function for CloudObject retrieve operations
    GetDataCallback  
    LoginCallback
    Callback function for CloudUser login requests
    LogoutCallback
    Callback function for CloudUser logout requests
    PasswordResetCallback
    Callback function for password reset requests.
    PushCallback
    Callback function for Push messages
    SaveCallback
    Callback function for CloudObject save operations.
    SignupCallback
    Callback function for CloudUser signup operations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CloudAuthException
    An Exception indicating that a Session failed to open or obtain new permissions.
    CloudException
    This is the base class for all exceptions of CloudEngine.
    CloudObjectException
    Exceptions related to CloudObject are instances of this class.
